platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: A terrific follow-up to our 2012 iPad Game of the Year, The Room Two continues the dark, foreboding tale introduced in its predecessor. Marvelously detailed graphics and eerie music make this first-person puzzler feel stunningly real, and as you travel from an ancient crypt to a sance room and beyond, youll love unlocking the secrets of every objectand learning more about your mysterious imprisonment.
